AllFactSheets is a List
    single select
    initially display search
    Display Fields
        SampleDocumentTemplate
        Description
        button of "<Attachment.Title>"
            view Attachment.File
            label is "Attachment"
            left align
            display as link
        Type
            sort order is ByType
                is default
        Template
        ForIDM
        HasInstructions
            link is InstructionsLink
        DerivedCreateDate
            label is "DateCreated"
    Instance Selection
        where (FactSheets
        and   NotObsolete)
    Actions
        action is Create
        action is Update
            hide when invalid
